<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Meter Inactivity Alert</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; margin: 0; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626, #991b1b); padding: 24px 32px;">
      <h1 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 22px;">⚠️ Meter Inactivity Alert</h1>
    </div>

    <!-- Body -->
    <div style="padding: 32px;">
      <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #333; margin-top: 0;">
        <strong>{{count}} meter(s)</strong> have been detected as <strong style="color: #dc2626;">inactive</strong>.
      </p>

      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #555;">
        These meters have not sent any events within the configured inactivity threshold.
        Please review the attached Excel report for full details including:
      </p>

      <ul style="font-size: 14px; color: #555; padding-left: 20px;">
        <li>Device ID</li>
        <li>Household ID (HHID)</li>
        <li>Last Connectivity Timestamp</li>
        <li>Inactive Since</li>
      </ul>

      <div style="background: #fef2f2; border: 1px solid #fecaca; border-radius: 6px; padding: 16px; margin: 20px 0;">
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #991b1b;">
          📎 <strong>Attached:</strong> Inactive_Meters_Report.xlsx
        </p>
      </div>

      <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #888; margin-bottom: 0;">
        Check performed at: <strong>{{checkTime}}</strong>
      </p>

      <div style="margin-top: 24px;">
        <a href="{{appUrl}}/live-monitoring/alerts"
           style="display: inline-block; background: #dc2626; color: #fff; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">
          View Alerts Dashboard →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div style="background: #f9fafb; padding: 16px 32px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
      <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; margin: 0; text-align: center;">
        This is an automated alert from the Meter Monitoring Platform.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
